          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SDS add-on to Support Plan helps people with mental health problems to plan in advance for how they will manage their SDS when their condition fluctuates and they become unwell.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
